data.title: CPS Dean’s List honors announced for Fall 2023
data.text:
A total of 649 undergraduate students had a GPA over 3.75–including 282 with a perfect 4.0–to earn dean’s list honors for the 2023 fall semester in the College of Professional Studies at the University of Wisconsin-Stevens Point. Congratulations to all!

CPS Dean’s List by Major (number of 4.0):

Accounting: 38 (18)

Business Administration: 68 (26)

Business Economics: 3 (0)

Clinical Lab Science: 19 (11)

Communication Sciences and Disorders: 48 (27)

Data Analytics: 16 (4)

Dietetics: 16 (4)

Early Childhood Education: 55 (20)

Elementary Education: 185 (88)

Family and Consumer Sciences: 28 (19)

Finance: 32 (15)

Health and Wellness Management: 1 (1)

Health Information Management and Technology: 1 (1)

Health Promotion and Wellness: 3 (1)

Health Science: 17 (6)

Health Science and Wellness: 54 (14)

Health Sciences (AAS): 1 (1)

Leadership and Project Management (AAS): 3 (2)

Management: 20 (13)

Marketing: 33 (11)

Nursing/Pre-Nursing: 18 (5)

Physical Education: 35 (16)

Special Education: 85 (47)

Sustainable Food and Nutrition: 2 (0)

CPS Dean’s List (* indicates 4.0):

Students must maintain full-time status and have GPA over 3.75 to earn honors.
